#

Spinach Artichoke Dip

30 min
$10
200 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

AppetizerDipParty Food

Description

A creamy, cheesy dip packed with flavor, perfect for parties or a cozy night in!

Ingredients

  • frozen spinach, thawed and drained: 1 cup
  • artichoke hearts, canned, drained and chopped: 1 cup
  • cream cheese, softened: 8 oz
  • sour cream: 1/2 cup
  • mayonnaise: 1/4 cup
  • parmesan cheese, grated: 1/2 cup
  • mozzarella cheese, shredded: 1/2 cup
  • garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
